                Nebraska's Online High School, and an internal event management system used by an internal office.</p>
            <details class="ic-experience_section-details">
                <summary>
                    <span>More Details</span>
                    {{> partials/icon
                        style="far"
                        icon="chevron-down"
                        size="xs"
                    }}
                </summary>
                <ul>
                    <li>Collaborated with designers, developers, and product owners to plan future work and gather
                        requirements</li>
                    <li>Documented user story details, acceptance criteria, and testing documentation in an agile/scrum
                        environment</li>
                    <li>Developed front-end in compliance with standardized coding principles and best practices</li>
                    <li>Met with back-end developers to discuss feature hand-off</li>
                    <li>Continuously tested and performed quality assurance of front-end / implemented features</li>
                    <li>Maintained front-end prototypes, design system components, and pattern library documentation
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </details>
        </div>
        <div class="ic-experience_section-item">
            <div class="ic-experience_section-marker">
                {{> partials/icon
                    style="fal"
                    icon="fire-alt"
                    size="lg"
                }}
            </div>
            <h4 class="ic-experience_section-location">Firespring</h4>
            <p class="ic-experience_section-caption">Front-End Web Developer</p>
            <p class="ic-experience_section-period">May 2017 &ndash; Oct 2018</p>
            <h5 class="ic-experience_section-subtitle">Responsibilities</h5>
            <p class="ic-experience_section-summary">Worked on a team of designers and front-end developers focused on
                setting up customer's websites, developing custom website themes, and maintaining websites for a
                proprietary CMS.</p>
            <details class="ic-experience_section-details">
                <summary>
                    <span>More Details</span>
                    {{> partials/icon
                        style="far"
                        icon="chevron-down"
                        size="xs"
                    }}
                </summary>
                <ul>
                    <li>Developed custom themes for small to medium businesses based on designer's mockups</li>
                    <li>Performed quality assurance testing and bug reporting for fellow developers</li>
                    <li>Fixed client bug reports and completed client requests</li>
                    <li>Documented front-end practices and worked with developers to improve our internal framework</li>
                    <li>Worked with customer service to set up clients in the CMS and migrated content from their
                        previous websites</li>
                </ul>
            </details>
        </div>
        <div class="ic-experience_section-item">
            <div class="ic-experience_section-marker">
                {{> partials/icon
                    style="fal"
                    icon="graduation-cap"
                    size="lg"
                }}
